[b]Source modules (q-flux):[/b]
[code]
crates/q-flux/src/
  main.rs          CLI, config loading, worker spawning, graceful shutdown
  config.rs        TOML config parsing (q-flux.toml)
  acceptor.rs      TLS accept with rustls, hot-reloadable SharedTlsConfig
  worker.rs        Per-core worker loop (own tokio runtime, own TcpListener)
  proxy.rs         HTTP/1.1 request forwarding, WebSocket detection
  upstream.rs      Per-worker connection pool, health-aware round-robin, super-cluster failover
  metrics.rs       Lock-free atomic counters, RateLimiter, MetricsSnapshot
  health.rs        Active health checker + inline auto-recovery
  admin.rs         Admin HTTP server (health, metrics, TLS reload)
  static_serve.rs  Static file serving for frontend assets
  access_log.rs    Structured JSON access logging with ring buffer
  tui.rs           Live terminal dashboard (ratatui)
  io_uring_loop.rs io_uring event loop (multishot accept, registered buffers)
  simd_parse.rs    AVX2/SSE4.2 HTTP header boundary detection
  h2_proxy.rs      HTTP/2 proxy module
  quic_proxy.rs    QUIC/HTTP/3 proxy via quinn
  libp2p_aware.rs  PeerTracker, circuit breaker, bandwidth tiers
[/code]


